Date: Wed, 26 Mar 2025 16:20:54 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 205/205] Show mapped and raw Dbus messages in Log services

Currently we have a flag, that enables mapping in the code, and if the
mapping is enabled, it will try to map an entry, and if it fails, it
will return an error to the requester. If it's disabled, it will read
data from DBus event and put to the log entry.

Testing:
Ran it in QEMU, fetched logs and raw and mapped are shown [1].

